sep=: As a user, I want to see which crates contain which items.
As a user, I want to see more links on the front page in addition to the navigation menu.
As a user, I want to see the contributions of each team member.
As a user, I want to see a list of all of the tools used to create the application.
As a user, I want to see why this site was created.
As a user, I want to see the name of the site on the front page.
As a PS4 user, I want to see player stats for PS4 players.
As an Xbox user, I want to see player stats for Xbox players.
As a PC user, I want to see player stats for Steam players.
As a user, I want to view information about the game the database is based on.
